    (cnfg P1 P2 P3 P4 P5 P6 P7 P8 (p wrtr18 N) P10 (sem S D T) X 1) /\ (band (mequals N D) (bnot (mequals N 0))) => (cnfg P1 P2 P3 P4 P5 P6 P7 P8 (p wrtr19 0) P10 (sem S D T) X 0),
    (cnfg P1 P2 P3 P4 P5 P6 P7 P8 (p wrtr19 0) P10 (sem S D T) X 0) => (cnfg P1 P2 P3 P4 P5 P6 P7 P8 (p wrtr20 0) P10 (sem S D T) 1 0),
    (cnfg P1 P2 P3 P4 P5 P6 P7 P8 (p wrtr20 0) P10 (sem S D T) X 0) /\ (band (bnot (mequals T (mplus D 2))) (mequals D2 (mplus D 2))) => (cnfg P1 P2 P3 P4 P5 P6 P7 P8 (p wrtr18 0) P10 (sem S D2 T) X 1),
